---

<Layout 
  title="Professional Business Card & Branding Design Services on Fiverr"
  description="Find expert designers for your business cards and brand identity on Fiverr. Get professional, print-ready designs that make a lasting impression."
>
  <Header />
  
  <main class="pt-24">
    <article class="container mx-auto px-6 max-w-4xl">
      <!-- Hero Section -->
      <div class="mb-12">
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-display font-bold mb-6">
          Professional Business Card & Branding Design Services on Fiverr
        </h1>
        <div class="flex items-center text-gray-400 text-sm mb-8">
          <time datetime="2025-01-15">January 15, 2025</time>
          <span class="mx-2">•</span>
          <span>10 min read</span>
        </div>
        <img 
          src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1634084462412-b54873c0a56d?auto=format&fit=crop&q=80&w=1200" 
          alt="Business Cards and Branding Materials"
          class="w-full rounded-xl mb-8"
        />
      </div>

      <!-- Content -->
      <div class="prose prose-invert prose-lg max-w-none">
        <h2>Why Professional Business Cards & Branding Matter</h2>
        <p>
          In today's digital age, having professional business cards and consistent branding is more important than ever. They serve as tangible representations of your business and help:
        </p>
        <ul>
          <li>Make memorable first impressions</li>
          <li>Build professional credibility</li>
          <li>Create brand recognition</li>
          <li>Stand out from competitors</li>
          <li>Facilitate networking and referrals</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>Why Choose Fiverr for Business Cards & Branding?</h2>
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 not-prose my-8">
          {[
            {
              title: "Professional Design",
              points: [
                "Expert designers",
                "Modern templates",
                "Print-ready files",
                "Quick turnaround"
              ]
            },
            {
              title: "Affordable Options",
              points: [
                "Competitive pricing",
                "Package deals",
                "Revision options",
                "No hidden fees"
              ]
            },
            {
              title: "Quality Assurance",
              points: [
                "Portfolio review",
                "Customer feedback",
                "File guarantees",
                "Support team"
              ]
            },
            {
              title: "Complete Branding",
              points: [
                "Full identity packages",
                "Style guidelines",
                "Multiple formats",
                "Source files"
              ]
            }
          ].map(section => (
            <div class="bg-dark-lighter p-6 rounded-lg">
              <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4">{section.title}</h3>
              <ul class="space-y-2">
                {section.points.map(point => (
                  <li class="flex items-center">
                    <span class="text-primary mr-2">✓</span>
                    <span class="text-gray-300">{point}</span>
                  </li>
                ))}
              </ul>
            </div>
          ))}
        </div>

        <h2>Top-Rated Business Card & Branding Designers</h2>
        <p>
          Here are some of our highest-rated designers who specialize in business cards and brand identity:
        </p>

        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6 not-prose my-8">
          {recommendedDesigners.map(designer => (
            <div class="bg-dark-lighter rounded-lg overflow-hidden">
              <img 
                src={designer.image} 
                alt={designer.title}
                class="w-full h-48 object-cover"
              />
              <div class="p-6">
                <div class="flex items-center mb-2">
                  <span class="text-yellow-400 mr-1">★</span>
                  <span class="text-sm text-gray-300">{designer.rating} ({designer.reviews} reviews)</span>
                </div>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">{designer.title}</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm mb-4">{designer.description}</p>
                <ul class="text-sm text-gray-400 mb-4">
                  {designer.features.map(feature => (
                    <li class="flex items-center mb-1">
                      <span class="text-primary mr-2">•</span>
                      {feature}
                    </li>
                  ))}
                </ul>
                <p class="text-primary font-semibold">{designer.price}</p>
                <p class="text-sm text-gray-400">Delivery: {designer.deliveryTime}</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          ))}
        </div>

        <h2>Business Card & Branding Design Pricing Guide</h2>
        <p>
          Understanding the different pricing tiers can help you choose the right package for your needs:
        </p>

        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 not-prose my-8">
          {pricingTiers.map(tier => (
            <div class="bg-dark-lighter p-6 rounded-lg">
              <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">{tier.name}</h3>
              <p class="text-primary font-bold text-2xl mb-4">{tier.price}</p>
              <ul class="space-y-2">
                {tier.features.map(feature => (
                  <li class="flex items-center">
                    <span class="text-primary mr-2">✓</span>
                    <span class="text-gray-300">{feature}</span>
                  </li>
                ))}
              </ul>
            </div>
          ))}
        </div>

        <h2>How to Order Business Cards & Branding on Fiverr</h2>
        <div class="space-y-8 my-8">
          {orderSteps.map((step, index) => (
            <div class="bg-dark-lighter p-6 rounded-lg">
              <div class="flex items-start">
                <span class="text-4xl font-bold text-primary mr-4">{index + 1}</span>
                <div>
                  <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">{step.title}</h3>
                  <p class="text-gray-300 mb-4">{step.description}</p>
                  <ul class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-2">
                    {step.tips.map(tip => (
                      <li class="flex items-center">
                        <span class="text-primary mr-2">•</span>
                        <span class="text-gray-400">{tip}</span>
                      </li>
                    ))}
                  </ul>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          ))}
        </div>

        <h2>Pro Tips for Getting the Best Results</h2>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Prepare Your Content:</strong> Have your contact information and brand assets ready.</li>
          <li><strong>Know Your Preferences:</strong> Collect examples of designs you like and dislike.</li>
          <li><strong>Consider Print Requirements:</strong> Specify any special printing needs or paper types.</li>
          <li><strong>Think Long-term:</strong> Consider how your branding will scale across different materials.</li>
        </ul>

        <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-primary/10 to-secondary/10 p-8 rounded-lg my-12">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Ready to Create Your Professional Brand Identity?</h2>
          <p class="mb-6">
            Browse our curated selection of top-rated business card and branding designers. Get professional, print-ready designs that make a lasting impression on your clients and partners.
          </p>
          <a 
            href="#top-designers" 
            class="inline-block bg-accent hover:bg-accent/90 text-white px-8 py-3 rounded-lg font-semibold transition-colors"
          >
            Browse Top Designers
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </article>
  </main>
</Layout>

<style>
  .prose {
    @apply text-gray-300;
  }
  .prose h2 {
    @apply text-white mt-12 mb-6;
  }
  .prose h3 {
    @apply text-white mt-8 mb-4;
  }
  .prose ul {
    @apply my-6;
  }
  .prose li {
    @apply mb-2;
  }
  .prose p {
    @apply mb-6;
  }
  .prose table {
    @apply text-gray-300;
  }
</style>